description: Make the most of ripe bananas with this easy recipe for banana cake topped with a delicious cream cheese frosting.
name: Easy Banana Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: To make the cream cheese frosting, use an electric mixer to beat cream cheese until smooth. Add icing sugar and beat until well combined. Place cake on a plate, spread with frosting and serve.
